snippet.textDisplay:
Guuyyss pls stop hating/attacking Daniel so much
I know we are all angry, sad, disappointed in Dan etc. but there is no reason to attack Dan so bad and even wish him the dead...
Like come on seriously ?
Every person makes mistakes.
Just imagine every time everyone you think they liked you wished you the dead when you did something wrong.
Nobody wants that and nobody deserves that !
Yes Daniel did a mistake but that doesn't give us the right to hate/harase him.
We are all humans !
We are all making mistakes !
It's important to let Daniel see his mistake (without hate) and let him work on himself so he can become a better person.
Daniel has his private life too and we all don't know whats going on in his life and mind.
Even if he post a video about his side we shouldn't keep on the hate after that.
It's going to make it worse for Daniel (and the Danplancrew, Stephen etc.) and will make the progress of learning from his mistake even more difficult.
You can unsub but attacking Daniel will make nothing better it will make everything worse for everyone.
Stephen said that nobody should attack Daniel but everyone is just jumping in a conclusion without even thinking about what Dan has to say or how he will feel.
If you don't want to stop attacking Dan then please stop it for Stephen and Hoshu.
I'm pretty sure they wouldn't wanted this to happen.
Nobody deserves that kind of treatment 💚
#lovefordaniel
#loveforeveryone
